6000|$|Morrison surrendered, {{himself to}} another season of cogitation, {{in which he}} {{probably}} found his vagueness growing upon him. He ended by fumbling in all his pockets, and bringing up from the last <b>a</b> crumpled <b>scrap</b> <b>of</b> <b>paper.</b> [...] "What you--what you say that?" ...|$|R
