60|$|Gregory knew that, at Wad Gamr's house, but few {{signs of}} the tragedy had been found when General Brackenbury's troops entered. Bloodstained visiting cards <b>of</b> Stewart's, <b>a</b> few <b>scraps</b> <b>of</b> <b>paper,</b> and <b>a</b> field glass had, alone, been discovered, besides the boxes <b>of</b> <b>papers.</b>|$|R
